title: GTA V Extracted (XBOX360)
description:
A fully extracted version of Grand Theft Auto V (XBOX360 version of GTA V).
Decrypt key is included as well as a RPF file extractor/browser and a texture browser.

You can not play GTA V on any platform with these files. They are purely for development and research.

The default.xex file is decrypted, decompressed and extracted, with a dev info file (For decompilation in ida pro)

The torrent is partially zipped, due to the max file limit on torrents. Just unzip levels.zip and common.zip.
